ARTICULOS:
Crear un registro
POST (http://localhost:3036/articulos/) 
EJ:
body:
{
"modelo": "23",
"color_id": 2,
"categorie": "sandalias",
"status": "active",
"id_autor": 1
} 
Actualizar por id 
PUT (http://localhost:3036/articulos/id)
EJ: (http://localhost:3036/articulos/2)
{
"modelo": "23",
"color_id": 2,
"categorie": "sandalias",
"status": "inactive",
"id_autor": 1
} 
Leer un registro por ID
GET (http://localhost:3036/articulos/id)
EJ: (http://localhost:3036/articulos/1)
DEVUELVE:
{
  "id": 1,
  "modelo": "Camisa Formal",
  "color_id": 1,
  "categorie": "Ropa",
  "status": "active",
  "id_autor": 1,
  "createdAt": "2024-11-26",
  "updatedAt": "2024-11-26"
}
